DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    VALUES('Orders'[Year])

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'Orders'[Year], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
  'Orders'[Year]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"2015"}, 'Orders'[Year])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
    TREATAS({"Canon imageCLASS 2200 Advanced Copier"}, 'Orders'[Product Name])

EVALUATE
  SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
    __DS0FilterTable,
    __DS0FilterTable2,
    "SumSales", IGNORE(CALCULATE(SUM('Orders'[Sales])))
  )

DEFINE
  VAR __H0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"Canon imageCLASS 2200 Advanced Copier"}, 'Orders'[Product Name])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"2015"}, 'Orders'[Year])

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Orders'[Segment],
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "SumSales", CALCULATE(SUM('Orders'[Sales])),
      "OrdersSumSales", IGNORE(
        CALCULATE(SUM('Orders'[Sales]), KEEPFILTERS(__H0FilterTable))
      )
    )

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, [SumSales], 0, 'Orders'[Segment], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  [SumSales] DESC, 'Orders'[Segment]
